Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:05.60,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Yuujirou-san, I'm sorry for being so cocky up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:09.36,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I'll do the meetings and draw the names.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:11.65,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,What brought this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:15.12,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I think that from everyone telling me I was a genius so much, I turned into a goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:19.34,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Well, that way I can be a lot more relaxed about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:24.24,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,And now becoming the number one author in Jack really isn't just a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:25.92,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:29.80,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,For the early report of chapter three, you're third!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:32.05,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter three was better?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:34.30,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It was different from how we read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:36.83,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:41.65,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,We made chapter five more interesting and got him to do meetings and names.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:47.31,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I'm going to be the most popular mangaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:47.31,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was glad that Eiji was drawing names now, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:50.02,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I came here for Shuujin's sake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.17,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to bring something back...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:20.94,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.03,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:23.53,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Crow True-Fist! {TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:24.75,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.54,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The most popular mangaka, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:31.45,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I become the number one most popular author in Jack,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:34.88,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}please give me the power to end one manga that I hate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:39.35,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Making Niizuma Eiji number one is my job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:41.93,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, if he becomes number one, we'll deal with that then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.89,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Last two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:47.22,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.72,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then I'll be here at 5 PM tomorrow to pick up chapter five.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.10,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,We can have a meeting after that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:53.98,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.86,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have it done by 5 PM, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.70,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. Sensei only has two pages left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.41,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll leave you guys to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:08.50,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Yuujirou-san, there's something I've been meaning to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.21,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:14.42,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Mangas appear in Jack by order of popularity, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.52,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't entirely in order by popularity,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:19.05,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,but if you exclude gag manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.45,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,well, I guess you could say the more popular mangas are farther forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:24.64,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,and the less popular mangas are more towards the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.25,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.81,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Even most other magazines do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:31.61,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I just think it's unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:37.61,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,The print order gives the readers a preconception that some mangas are popular and some aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:41.28,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a lot of kids who feel they have to read the same mangas as everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.41,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I think making the order a rotation would be more fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:44.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What're you saying, Fukuda-san?{\i0} {This is said over Fukuda's last line.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:48.45,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,That way, you can be sure the questionnaire results will subtly change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:51.71,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Appearance order creates a disparity in the manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.85,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Tell you what...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:56.37,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,you can say all the self-righteous things you want once you've been serialized and taken the world by storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:58.67,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Please just calm down and listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.59,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only giving you an opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:04.34,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, I'm not happy about how it's just the questionnaire results
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.55,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,that determine which mangas are popular and which get canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:09.75,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,The editorial department should decide which mangas are popular and which aren't themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:13.81,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Doing it this way is like saying you have no ability to do it yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:18.44,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Fu–Fukuda-kun, you'd better make sure not to say things like that at the editorial department.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:22.70,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think everyone has potential, so I'll hear you out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.69,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Then listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.12,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,If a manga doesn't get flashy from the start, particularly if it doesn't reach a climax in chapter one,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.36,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,then it ends up on the course to cancellation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:32.65,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,That's because cancellation could already be decided as soon as chapter three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:37.87,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, everyone is too scared to draw a manga that starts out subdued and gradually gets more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:41.00,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,That results in every work having somewhat the same flavor as all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.77,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,If the editorial department had enough confidence in it to start it as a new series,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:48.88,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,then don't you think they should at least watch over it until there's a collected volume of it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:54.02,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,If we gave that sort of leeway to every new series, no more than five new series would start per year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:56.12,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,But I think there are ones like that;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:59.23,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,mangas that start out subdued, but get gradually more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:03.33,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Like where the protagonist starts out completely unskilled but works really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:07.07,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,With the current system, you can't get popular by starting out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:10.46,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well even in that type of manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:13.54,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,you need to come up with something to interesting before it gets canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:17.15,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Fukuda-kun, are you drawing one like that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:17.96,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Ah,no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:23.44,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm writing a name in which the protagonist wins right from chapter one, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:29.47,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Then all you're saying is if you get serialized, you'd like us to be patient with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:33.61,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say that looking objectively at how the magazine does things is bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:36.18,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,but that's the editorial department's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:39.56,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,You should be concentrating on your own work first and foremost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.60,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.78,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.47,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,You've moved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.42,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the order rotation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:49.25,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.32,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:52.45,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I never would  have thought of something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:56.75,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of sounds like everyone's only concerned with doing well in the questionnaires.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.21,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good for manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.46,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,If you draw manga only for the sake of questionnaire results, your manga will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.33,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:06.46,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,In Jack, my favorite manga is {\i1}To Love-Ru{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:07.67,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! I didn't expect that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.02,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,But it does really badly in the questionnaires.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.30,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.55,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.16,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda ecchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:18.06,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,so most people don't want anyone to know it would be one they choose in their "three most interesting".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.21,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:23.32,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,even I've sent in questionnaires without writing in the numbers for mangas I liked, such as{\i1} Ichigo 100%{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.23,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's sent in questionnaires...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:31.05,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,There are probably even grade schoolers who ask their parents to mail the questionnaires for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:34.13,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,So it must be hard for them to choose To Love-Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:35.00,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.66,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, because it's so ecchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:41.56,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,But {\i1}To Love-Ru{\i0} is a man's shounen manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.46,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we understand perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.00,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But I think with {\i1}To Love-Ru{\i0}, they take that into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.00,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:49.44,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It has center color pages a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.97,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,And I think the volumes sell well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:51.98,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:53.53,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:57.09,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,If it sells, I want them to pump out more color pages and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:07:00.56,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if there are too many ecchi images on the cover, the magazine's image will—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.14,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:04.39,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Manga being a little ecchi, having panty shots and stuff is part of a boy's romanticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:06.20,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,And men's dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.78,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,"We'll change Jack." I kind of understand that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.32,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,What you're saying is really interesting, Fukuda-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.31,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds beneficial!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.64,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:19.87,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the contents of the manga have to change, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:23.11,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,First, you'd need to give the covers a rotation by series.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.00,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,That would make it fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:29.59,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,And the magazine should open with pull-out gravure shots of idols or posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.12,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:32.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,That's just your personal preference, Fukuda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.67,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:35.41,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,All the other magazines do that, so Jack should too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:36.76,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Shounen needs idols!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:37.98,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, that's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:40.39,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I think they take pride in the fact that they compete with just manga without any gravure shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.46,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.23,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Then just throw out that stupid pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:43.81,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:48.04,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,Could you argue about this after we've finished the manuscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:49.32,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming to get it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.81,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, s-sorry. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:55.18,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I got a little caught up in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.16,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun, how much is left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:03.71,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm done, but how much time do you think you'll need to finish up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.38,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Those backgrounds really give a good impression! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.69,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:13.16,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai-san's technique is extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:18.18,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Since coming here, I've probably learned the most from watching Nakai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:20.07,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to compliment me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:22.90,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get to the fill-in inking, whiting, and tones, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:23.98,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:29.52,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it'll really be all right for me to leave it to you guys from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:35.00,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Going to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.70,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to sleep now, you probably won't be up by the time Yuujirou comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:38.95,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Well yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.87,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,After he comes to get it, the next thing you were going to do was have a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.54,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll make sure to have it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:48.86,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Before you go to sleep, you should think about what kinds of things you want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.83,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:54.04,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise Yuujirou-san will control the pace of the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:55.43,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll have just woken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.89,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.65,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Another
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:05.56,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,ally,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.60,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:07.89,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,put one in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:08.66,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:11.15,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I was only helping with the decisions for chapter five.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.74,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'll put one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.50,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,My notebook... notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.87,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Where did I put that notebook... notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.91,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:22.54,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:24.16,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:27.50,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,They're important notebooks, so I put them in my drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:31.17,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it should be a character that can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:34.51,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I drew a sparrow manga in my fourth year of elementary school. I can use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.97,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun, are those character designs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:44.65,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I've been drawing manga ever since I started elementary school, so I have plenty I can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:47.75,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,My house in Aomori was pretty far in the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:51.31,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,so it took over half an hour to get to someone in my grade's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:54.52,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone would play video games and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:58.32,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,but the place to buy them was far away too, and I didn't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.80,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,So all I ever did was draw manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:03.84,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,But that was what I always had the most fun doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.71,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guys that end up being mangakas...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.51,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,usually draw stuff in their notebooks starting from when they're little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:13.33,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,They get pretty good, so they end up wanting to be mangakas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:14.30,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:17.91,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Crow is a character I made when I was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.38,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Elementary school?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{The opening theme and all are exactly the same as in episode 1.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:46.06,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom, it's starting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.81,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, I'm coming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.91,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You sure are good, Moritaka-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:02.40,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah... I'd always drawn manga up until Uncle died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.82,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both at home and at school...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.28,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really enjoyed it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:09.33,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So much that I would lose track of time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:11.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Losing myself in it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.63,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've loved manga ever since I was a kid,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.04,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}becoming a mangaka is my dream.{\i0} {It's worth mentioning that in some later chapter it's discussed how Shuujin came up with his dream of becoming a mangaka later in life. So I altered this line from the original episode which said "it's always been my dream". Fix that for the BD release, too.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:21.13,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even Shuujin should have something he would really like to draw.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:28.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-san, sorry, but would it be okay if I stepped down as your assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:38.81,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,You caught on to something, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:40.78,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:43.83,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear it. Then go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:46.45,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you can't just quit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:49.46,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,At least help us finish chapter five before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:50.91,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,We came up with it together, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.66,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:57.14,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I can take care of Niizuma-kun even if it's by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.50,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.59,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.17,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if Fukuda-kun quits later, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:07.35,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I would feel bad if you were doing this all alone, so I'll stay here until I get serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:09.98,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely gonna get serialized too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:15.59,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,What a mangaka needs is the willpower and stamina to persistently keep drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:16.85,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'll give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.48,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Th–Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:24.29,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely get serialized too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.48,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be in Jack together with all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:28.22,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's hurry and get this done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:28.49,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:03.57,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do, they all have the same sort of feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:07.70,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Really, trying to display originality isn't mainstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:11.03,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh, Azuki's anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{The end of some line comes out in the end, which I can't hear, obviously. ALL of these lines are barely audible. After listening to them a ton of times this is what I got.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:17.14,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,With our experiences every day being lucky, {rakkii da na maichi no keiken}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:20.42,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,and each one of us being liked by all.{hitori hitori moteru ne}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Our hopes of yesterday... {kinou kibou ni wa...}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{The CD comes out in March sometime, there aren't any lyrics online I could use to figure these background lines out until then.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.48,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Azuki will appear in this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.82,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,She had four lines last time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:29.54,Main,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Sei Visual, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:31.12,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.65,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, you have to get to your job early tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.37,Main,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I have tomorrow off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:37.90,Main,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, enjoy your show. {If you have anyone who can check this line, do so. It's INCREDIBLY inaudible.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:38.93,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:46.50,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,There we are, chapter five. {KmE: I think this one isn't said}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.42,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-eight pages, fully accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.66,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.55,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.74,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Yuujirou-san, let's have our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:55.81,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,All right! {KmE: This wasn't on the script put he clearly says something like "Yeah!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:15:00.30,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I know it's only been a little while, but I'm very grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:02.35,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,It really has been short.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:05.17,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping you could stay at least another two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.06,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many assistants anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:09.87,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun's a fast worker, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:11.15,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.60,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,It will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:15.77,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,For a while, it was actually just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.72,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,Two people will be plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.60,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Something feels kind of different about you, Nakai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.47,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.86,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please look at a name I'm drawing next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:31.32,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's changed. His character's changed drastically!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:38.02,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, guys that end up being mangakas...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.91,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,usually draw stuff in their notebooks starting from when they're little kids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:44.12,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crow is a character I made when I was in elementary school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:47.82,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The feelings I had when I first wanted to be a mangaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.69,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My favorite character from back then!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:51.90,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.05,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One I think Shuujin would like to write.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.68,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something we can synchronize with!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.35,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So what was it you wanted to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:02.51,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. You'll really enjoy it once you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:03.98,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:05.81,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,My room is on the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:07.93,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Both of my parents are at work,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:09.85,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,and my little brother isn't here because of his clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:14.98,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aw, man... I don't think I've been in a girl's house since kindergarten.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:24.04,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her room's actually a lot more feminine than I imagined...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:25.74,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:28.26,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I've received emails from companies about my cell phone novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:30.17,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, that's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:34.87,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,"We've looked at your work 'Awanai Koi', Miyoshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:34.87,TL Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Awanai Koi = Love Apart
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:36.87,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,We hope you will write further continuations,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:43.37,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,and based their popularity on our homepage, we would like to distribute them on mobile devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.24,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:47.17,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I'm the one who wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:51.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did use Mashiro and Azuki as models for it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.16,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-sensei, please write a continuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:56.52,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:59.29,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a manga name to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:02.37,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, if you wanted to show this to me, couldn't you have just forwarded it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.22,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.41,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted us to be happy about it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:08.33,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:11.85,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.67,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Then you could have just come to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.80,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But your big brother's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.21,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Just because it's summer vacation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:18.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And because he's got today off from his part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.87,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Can't it just be us two?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.98,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can help you out a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:26.94,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,but I definitely can't write the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.35,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that battle stories are always difficult, and it's been a hard battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:31.19,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But what I'm doing is manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:32.75,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.70,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't you write out a scenario here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.45,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You can use my computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.01,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.62,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.95,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Then please write!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:47.66,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,At least until my parents come home...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.10,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.96,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to need to close your email to write anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:52.75,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.26,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a distribution site.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:59.30,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,It has what was sent in to that home site.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:03.23,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,They sure take stories for a lot of genres.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:04.18,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.56,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.86,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:14.66,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Where's grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:17.64,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He went to the hot spring with our neighbor Takayama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:18.87,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:23.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a little again, but I earned some money, so pass this to Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.72,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Give him that and all we've made so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:27.66,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you do, we've fought hard to get that money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:33.09,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:35.20,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,And so many...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:39.95,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Man, these suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:40.93,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:44.40,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they were a little better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:46.90,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:49.85,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Competing to be number one in the world using suspiciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.10,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain, in here...{KmE: This isn't translated.}{Translated by Z4kku.  Lament, suckers!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:55.92,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No, not this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:59.65,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I like the cheater detective in this, so I drew him again in another notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:07.91,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TL Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Sagishi Tantei Hikake = Con Man Detective Hikake {Time this... -_-}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:12.33,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The con man who would catch criminals there was no evidence against by making some up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:18.09,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shuujin mostly had manga at his house, but there were mystery novels too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:21.08,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were fixated on battle manga, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:24.58,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a detective manga is the mainstream of mainstreams in shounen magazines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.40,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it's Shuujin, he can do this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.85,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, this is what he'd be best at!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:37.27,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:39.40,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.60,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get him up to date with how my dream's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:43.83,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:44.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:49.88,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Miyoshi received a response from a company,\N asking her to write more of her cell phone novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:52.54,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's really amazing, and it's all thanks to you and Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:55.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see yesterday's Sei Visual?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:58.32,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no. Azuki told me she wasn't going to be in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:00.20,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I did manage to record it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:02.67,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Since Azuki appeared, she's been a big subject on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:07.38,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It could be just a matter of time until she really gets popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:08.75,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:10.82,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Miyoshi's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:12.15,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,And the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:13.62,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:16.46,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Takagi, that's a good line!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:19.86,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin, I don't want to say it at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:22.24,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:23.78,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you with Miyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:28.28,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because I like her, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:32.12,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're neglecting the name because of that, it's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:34.46,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean {\i1}neglecting{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.33,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I've been going all-out, working on it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:39.38,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,With Miyoshi and at her house?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:41.95,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:45.99,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it natural to want to be with someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:48.22,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you and Azuki aren't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:54.91,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You might be right. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:58.22,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But it's already August.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:00.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:02.03,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You're really going to finish it before the end of summer vacation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.53,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll contact you when I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:06.11,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:08.10,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.10,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:17.17,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I... Even I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.10,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}want to be with Azuki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:51.57,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe she's busy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.36,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He did say she's getting popular.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.37,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Azuki...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:04.28,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}are we slowly drifting apart?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:07.50,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like Shuujin and I are while he's with Miyoshi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:30.99,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Azuki...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:33.57,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.57,0:22:34.45,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The workplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.80,0:22:36.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've decided.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.40,0:22:40.84,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Shuujin hasn't finished a name by the end of summer vacation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:42.98,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll draw a manga alone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:45.43,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For Azuki's sake, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ending}
