Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.84,0:24:18.26,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Hattori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.56,0:24:20.57,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that? Just call me Yuujirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.57,0:24:22.35,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,But your name's Hattori, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.16,0:24:25.06,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Together and Alone. {That's also the title.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.36,0:24:28.36,Main,Hattoris,0000,0000,0000,,Double Hattoris are the bridge to your dreams!
